  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump up into the seat of a high octane monster sized big rig and welcome to the arcade style cargo delivery racing chaos game that is Monster Trucking. Speed and precision is key while you maneuver the city streets as you try not to lose control of your trailer or cargo. Keep that pedal down and boost your way to as many deliveries as possible. While in transit all destruction and chaos you cause will count towards your next delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/d26b3edd69b4b1342b8574540327c29b.webp?t=1750911673\" width=150 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Points are accumulated for each trailer delivered, cargo delivered, stunts while hauling and finally destruction along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/ecd67dcb94dc50c2ce169b240c1f9ea3.poster.avif?t=1750911673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/ecd67dcb94dc50c2ce169b240c1f9ea3.webm?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/ecd67dcb94dc50c2ce169b240c1f9ea3.mp4?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/54dfb41b432db48b6590c3d1201af357.webp?t=1750911673\" width=290 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High risk high reward for all destruction caused along the way can net big bonuses but don't lose control of that cargo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/a670e8e5277624ae1c07390d2e772a65.poster.avif?t=1750911673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/a670e8e5277624ae1c07390d2e772a65.webm?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/a670e8e5277624ae1c07390d2e772a65.mp4?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump up into the seat of a high octane monster sized big rig and welcome to the arcade style cargo delivery racing chaos game that is Monster Trucking. Speed and precision is key while you maneuver the city streets as you try not to lose control of your trailer or cargo. Keep that pedal down and boost your way to as many deliveries as possible. While in transit all destruction and chaos you cause will count towards your next delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/d26b3edd69b4b1342b8574540327c29b.webp?t=1750911673\" width=150 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Points are accumulated for each trailer delivered, cargo delivered, stunts while hauling and finally destruction along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/ecd67dcb94dc50c2ce169b240c1f9ea3.poster.avif?t=1750911673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/ecd67dcb94dc50c2ce169b240c1f9ea3.webm?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/ecd67dcb94dc50c2ce169b240c1f9ea3.mp4?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/54dfb41b432db48b6590c3d1201af357.webp?t=1750911673\" width=290 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High risk high reward for all destruction caused along the way can net big bonuses but don't lose control of that cargo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/a670e8e5277624ae1c07390d2e772a65.poster.avif?t=1750911673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/a670e8e5277624ae1c07390d2e772a65.webm?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412240/extras/a670e8e5277624ae1c07390d2e772a65.mp4?t=1750911673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
